Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗艦內壓力上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一到第五號引擎沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡航速度維持在5
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到底在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是戰爭啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡並不是學校！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經完全覺醒了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.22,0:00:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
