Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛翔 - 犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
